These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
2 different games are played: snooker, canasta
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, singing
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, white
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia
House: cape-cod, tower
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, dunhill
1. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
2. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person who likes ivory##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person who growstulip##6
4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
5. the person who likes white is not to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##8
6. the tower house is not the ritmeester-smoker##6
7. the person playing snooker is the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | coffee      |
| Game          | canasta | snooker   |
| Hobby         | singing    | board-games |
| Color           | ivory     | white    |
| Flower   | zinnia    | tulip       |
| House   | cape-cod    | tower        |
| Cigar     | ritmeester     | dunhill        |

